                    <h4>S-TIER: Temper First</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Bone Skill Damage:</strong> Direct multiplier to Bone Spear and Bone Prison. Your primary damage stat. Stack as much as possible.</li>
                        <li><strong>Critical Strike Damage:</strong> Maximizes burst during guaranteed crit windows from Deathless Visage. Target 200%+ total Crit Damage.</li>
                        <li><strong>Vulnerable Damage:</strong> With Bone Prison applying Vulnerable, this is a permanent multiplier during burst windows.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="tier tier-a">
                    <h4>A-TIER: High Priority</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Cooldown Reduction:</strong> Reduces Bone Prison and Blood Wave cooldowns. Essential for burst window frequency.</li>
                        <li><strong>Maximum Life:</strong> Your primary defensive stat alongside Ossified Essence shields. Target 10,000+ for Pit pushing.</li>
                        <li><strong>Critical Strike Chance:</strong> Important until you reach 60%+ with gear. Grasping Veins covers some, but more is always better.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="tier tier-b">
                    <h4>B-TIER: Fill Remaining Slots</h4>
