                    <p style="color: #a0a0a0; font-size: 0.85rem; margin-top: 8px;">Essence glyph increases damage based on your current Essence amount. Maintain high Essence for the damage bonus, then dump Essence during Bone Prison burst windows. This board provides additional life and damage nodes for survivability.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="paragon-board">
