                    <p style="color: #a0a0a0; font-size: 0.85rem; margin-top: 8px;">Exploit increases damage to Vulnerable enemies. Since Bone Prison applies Vulnerable, this glyph is always active during burst windows. Bone Graft board's Legendary node provides additional Bone skill damage scaling.</p>
