            <div class="section">
                <h2>Combat Rotation</h2>
                <p>The rotation is all about setting up and executing your Bone Prison burst combo. Master the timing and sequence to maximize damage during the guaranteed crit window.</p>

                <ol class="rotation-steps">
                    <li class="rotation-step">
                        <div>
                            <p><strong style="color: #d4af37;">Corpse Tendrils to Group</strong></p>
                            <p style="color: #a0a0a0; font-size: 0.85rem;">Start by using Corpse Tendrils to pull all nearby enemies together and apply Vulnerable. This groups enemies tightly so your Bone Prison and Bone Spear hit maximum targets. Grasping Veins grants Crit Chance for 6 seconds, setting up your burst window.</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="rotation-step">
                        <div>
                            <p><strong style="color: #d4af37;">Bone Prison on Grouped Pack</strong></p>
                            <p style="color: #a0a0a0; font-size: 0.85rem;">Cast Bone Prison on the grouped enemies. With Deathless Visage, enemies inside the prison take guaranteed Critical Strikes from your Bone skills for the duration. Dreadful Bone Prison also applies Vulnerable, stacking with Corpse Tendrils. This is your burst window -- everything that follows must happen before Bone Prison expires.</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="rotation-step">
                        <div>
                            <p><strong style="color: #d4af37;">Spam Bone Spear Inside Prison</strong></p>
                            <p style="color: #a0a0a0; font-size: 0.85rem;">Dump all your Essence into Bone Spear during the Bone Prison window. Every Bone Spear is a guaranteed crit thanks to Deathless Visage. Paranormal Bone Spear breaks apart and pierces, hitting multiple enemies. This is your primary burst damage -- land as many Bone Spears as possible before the prison expires.</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="rotation-step">
                        <div>
                            <p><strong style="color: #d4af37;">Blood Wave for Sustain</strong></p>
                            <p style="color: #a0a0a0; font-size: 0.85rem;">During the Bone Prison window, cast Blood Wave for additional burst damage and massive healing. Prime Blood Wave grants Overpower on your next attack, which you use on a Bone Spear. Supreme Blood Wave reduces the cooldown on kills, allowing faster burst windows.</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="rotation-step">
                        <div>
                            <p><strong style="color: #d4af37;">Corpse Explosion Follow-Up</strong></p>
                            <p style="color: #a0a0a0; font-size: 0.85rem;">After Bone Spear kills generate corpses inside the prison, spam Corpse Explosion for additional AoE burst. Plagued Corpse Explosion leaves damaging fields that finish off stragglers. Blood Moon Breeches boosts Corpse Explosion Crit Damage for massive explosions.</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="rotation-step">
                        <div>
                            <p><strong style="color: #d4af37;">Bone Prison Explosion Finisher</strong></p>
                            <p style="color: #a0a0a0; font-size: 0.85rem;">With Shattered Spirit Aspect, Bone Prison explodes when it ends, dealing massive AoE damage. Let the prison expire naturally to trigger the explosion. This finishes off remaining enemies and clears the area.</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="rotation-step">
                        <div>
                            <p><strong style="color: #d4af37;">Decrepify -- Auto-Applied</strong></p>
                            <p style="color: #a0a0a0; font-size: 0.85rem;">With Aspect of the Cursed Aura, Decrepify automatically applies to all nearby enemies. Abhorrent Decrepify triggers CDR on cursed enemy kills, reducing your Bone Prison and Blood Wave cooldowns. The more enemies you kill during your burst, the faster your next combo comes back.</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <h2>Tips & Advanced Play</h2>

                <div class="tip-card">
                    <strong>Timing is Everything</strong>
                    <p>Your burst window is dictated by Bone Prison duration. With Deathless Visage, you have extended time, but you must land all your Bone Spears before the prison expires. Practice the timing: Tendrils &rarr; Prison &rarr; 4-5 Bone Spears &rarr; Blood Wave &rarr; Explosions.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="tip-card">
                    <strong>Essence Management</strong>
                    <p>Bone Spear costs significant Essence. Maintain high Essence before casting Bone Prison so you can spam Bone Spear during the guaranteed crit window. If you run out of Essence mid-burst, your damage plummets. Essence glyph helps by granting bonus damage when at high Essence.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="tip-card">
                    <strong>Cooldown Windows</strong>
                    <p>This build is cooldown-dependent. Bone Prison and Blood Wave have long cooldowns. Between burst windows, focus on generating corpses, positioning, and waiting for cooldowns. Abhorrent Decrepify CDR helps -- the more enemies you kill during your burst, the faster your cooldowns return.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="tip-card">
                    <strong>Boss Strategy</strong>
                    <p>Against bosses, Bone Prison traps the boss in place. Use Corpse Tendrils first to apply Vulnerable and Grasping Veins Crit Chance, then cast Bone Prison and unload all your Bone Spears. Blood Wave during the window for massive single-target burst. Boss fights are where this build shines -- guaranteed crits on a stationary target.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="tip-card">
                    <strong>Positioning for Maximum Hits</strong>
                    <p>Bone Spear pierces with Ebonpiercer. Position yourself so that your Bone Spears travel through the entire Bone Prison, hitting every enemy inside. Aim from one edge of the prison to the other to maximize pierce hits.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="tip-card">
                    <strong>Ossified Essence Shields</strong>
                    <p>Every 100 Essence spent generates a bone shield. During your Bone Spear spam, you generate multiple shields that protect you. This is your primary survivability tool during burst windows when you are stationary and vulnerable.</p>
                </div>
